   Perrakis, Daniel D. B., Nat Resources Canada, Canadian Forest Serv, 506 West Burnside Rd, Victoria, BC V8Z IM5, Canada.
   Alexander, Martin E., Wild Rose Fire Behav, 180-50434 Range Rd 232, Leduc Cty, AB T4X 0L1, Canada.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.ecoinf.2024.102711},
EarlyAccessDate = {JUL 2024},
Article-Number = {102711},
Keywords = {Wildfire behaviour; Crown fire; Generative adversarial networks; Random
   Forest; TabPFN; XGBoost; AutoGluon},
Keywords-Plus = {FIRE; MODEL},
