   Dai, Zhihua, Anhui Normal Univ, Sch Ecol \& Environm, Wuhu 241002, Peoples R China.
   Liu, Fei, Zhejiang Univ, Zhejiang Key Lab Agr Remote Sensing \& Informat Tec, Hangzhou 310058, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.jhazmat.2026.141490},
EarlyAccessDate = {FEB 2026},
