   Papadopoulos, George; Espejo-Garcia, Borja; Fountas, Spyros, Agr Univ Athens, Sch Environm \& Agr Engn, Dept Nat Resources Management \& Agr Engn, Lab Agr Engn, Athens 11855, Greece.
   Zafeiriou, Ioannis; Georgiou, Evgenia, Agr Univ Athens, Lab Soil Sci \& Agr Chem, Athens 11855, Greece.
   Oikonomou, Antonia, Agr Univ Athens, Sch Environm \& Agr Engn, Dept Nat Resources \& Agr Engn, Lab Geol \& Minerol, 75 Iera Odos Str, Athens 11855, Greece.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.atech.2025.101732},
