   Liu, Chun, Univ Sci \& Technol China, Affiliated Hosp 1, Hefei, Anhui, Peoples R China.
   Gao, Frankliu, Univ Washington, Michael G Foster Sch Business, Box 353200, Seattle, WA 98195 USA.},
