   Nunes, Bruno Pereira, Univ Illinois, Dept Hlth \& Kinesiol, Urbana, IL, Italy.
   Schuch, Helena Silveira, Univ Queensland, Fac Hlth \& Behav Sci, Sch Dent, Brisbane, Australia.
   Demarco, Flavio Fernando, Radboud Univ Nijmegen, Med Ctr, Dept Dent, Nijmegen, Netherlands.},
