   Ding, Xiao-Hui, Chinese Peoples Liberat Army Gen Hosp, Med Ctr 1, Dept Pathol, Beijing, Peoples R China.
   Guo, Ai-Tao, Chinese Peoples Liberat Army Gen Hosp, Dept Pathol, Med Ctr 3, Beijing, Peoples R China.
